Package: scAgentKit
Type: Package
Title: Human-in-the-Loop, Auditable scRNA-seq Toolkit
Version: 0.4.0
Authors@R: person(given = "Changhao", family = "Kan",
                  email = "kch_ynu@163.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Experimental single-cell RNA-seq toolkit covering quality
    control, integration, dimensionality reduction, clustering, annotation,
    and sub-annotation. Built on agentomicsCore, it supports optional
    model-assisted decisions while retaining analyst review, decision
    records, parameters, figures, and generated script snippets. Includes
    cycling-cluster lineage cues, structured contamination prompts, hybrid
    confidence heuristics, marker-citation checks, and best-effort token
    usage capture when providers return usage metadata.
